{% extends "_includes/default.njk" %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy — Trading Assistant{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900 text-slate-200 px-6 py-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">The Short Version</h2>
      <p>We don't track you. We don't collect personal data beyond what is needed to run the app. There are no analytics and no third-party trackers.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">No Tracking</h2>
      <p>This website does not use any analytics services, tracking pixels, or monitoring scripts. We don't use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any similar tools. Your browsing activity is not recorded or analyzed.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Cookies</h2>
      <p>The Trading Assistant app uses a session cookie to keep you logged in. This cookie is strictly functional — it exists only to maintain your authenticated session. We do not use any tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party cookies.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Account Data</h2>
      <p>When you create an account, we store an email address and an encrypted password. This is only used to log you in — we never send emails, newsletters, or notifications to it. Feel free to use a fake email. We do not collect names, phone numbers, addresses, or any other personal information. Your trading data (levels, alerts, settings) is stored to provide the service and is not shared with anyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Trading Assistant integrates with external services to function (charting providers, font hosting, cryptocurrency exchanges). We have no control over the privacy practices of these third parties and recommend reviewing their own privacy policies.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Changes</h2>
      <p>If this policy ever changes, the update date at the top of this page will reflect it.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
{% endblock %}
